imming in 2004 in Athens whenMichael Phelpsburst onto the scene.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9076583554876093e-15, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, 20 years later, it is an absolute dream to have another front row seat to watch our incredible athletes -- not to mention all of the Wahoos.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute dream\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"another front row seat\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"our incredible athletes\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wahoos\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a UVA alum, it is great to see their success.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.965074246520788, \"rank\": 0.03361394680658785, \"text\": \"UVA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their success\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the first time we will have a red carpet for the Opening Ceremony, and I am excited that I will be there interviewing the many celebrities in attendance.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2075, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.99999285