": 4333}, {\"ngram\": \"these remarkable stories\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4367}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a privilege to be a part of showcasing the extraordinary moments of these athletes as they continue to inspire the next generation, especially as we celebrate the rise of women's sports on the Olympic stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a privilege\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4397}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4410}, {\"ngram\": \"the extraordinary moments\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4450}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"the next generation\", \"from\": 4497, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4571}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samantha Peszek - Gymnastics Analyst \\\"There is something special about the buzz in an Olympic city.\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4643, \"to\": 4652}, {\"ngram\": \"the buzz\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4675}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic city\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited for THAT\\u2026the camaraderie between athletes representing their county and their fans, the intense and inspirational athleticism at the highest level, and watching athletes' dreams come true\\u2026it's moments like this that I know I will remember for the rest of my life.\\\"\", \"from\": 4697, \"to\": 4974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the camaraderie\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4734}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4743, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"their county\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4777}, {\"ngram\": \"their fans\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4792}, {\"ngram\": \"the intense and inspirational athleticism\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4835}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' dreams\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4887}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4910}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 4961}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 4972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Wilkinson, Diving Analyst \\\"I am really excited to see the Olympics in such an iconic city!\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 5075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laura Wilkinson\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4993}, {\"ngram\": \"Diving Analyst\", \"from\": 4995, \"to\": 5009}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"such an iconic city\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always love watching diving and am really looking forward to some tough competitions full of insanely difficult dives, especially from the men.\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"some tough competitions\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5162}, {\"ngram\": \"insanely difficult dives\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5195}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if I can sneak out of the pool for an event, I would love to watchSimone Bilesagain or be in the beach volleyball venue right under the Eiffel Tower.\\\"\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 5248, \"to\": 5256}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 5261, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"watchSimone Bilesagain\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5309}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach volleyball venue\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5345}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 5358, \"to\": 5374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"*** In Paris this summer, the world's greatest athletes will compete against the backdrop of one of the most beautiful cities in the world